EN:
Library system:

-TASKS-
..........
+ logging into the system
- ability to add books (title, author, isbn)
- searching for books - the user enters the title or author or isbn (may be incomplete information) - displays a list of records for each book. show whether it is rented, if so, show information about the person renting it out and the date of departure and return.
- borrowing books, (the period lasts 2 weeks) - please provide the name and surname of the borrower...
- search for items Fr. together with the person and from when to when
- search for items Fr. for which the delivery date has passed along with the information about the axle
- search all books
..........


-TECHNOLOGIES-
..........
- maven
- database
- hashing for login
- if possible - use streams
- use of singletons
- tests for methods (not all)
..........
